<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263504.2017.1419996" author="Bartolucci, F" journalOrPublisher="Plant Biosystems" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="179 - 303" refId="B6" refString="Bartolucci, F, Peruzzi, L, Galasso, G, Albano, A, Alessandrini, A, Ardenghi, NMG, Astuti, G, Bacchetta, G, Ballelli, S, Banfi, E, Barberis, G, Bernardo, L, Bouvet, D, Bovio, M, Cecchi, L, Di Pietro, R, Domina, G, Fascetti, S, Fenu, G, Festi, F, Foggi, B, Gallo, L, Gottschlich, G, Gubellini, L, Iamonico, D, Iberite, M, Jimenez-Mejias, P, Lattanzi, E, Marchetti, D, Martinetto, E, Masin, RR, Medagli, P, Passalacqua, NG, Peccenini, S, Pennesi, R, Pierini, B, Poldini, L, Prosser, F, Raimondo, FM, Roma-Marzio, F, Rosati, L, Santangelo, A, Scoppola, A, Scortegagna, S, Selvaggi, A, Selvi, F, Soldano, A, Stinca, A, Wagensommer, RP, Wilhalm, T, Conti, F, 2018. An updated checklist of the vascular flora native to Italy. Plant Biosystems 152 (2): 179 - 303, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1080/11263504.2017.1419996" title="An updated checklist of the vascular flora native to Italy." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/11263504.2017.1419996" volume="152" year="2018">Bartolucci et al. (2018)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.410.1.1" author="Peruzzi, L" journalOrPublisher="Phytotaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 215" refId="B30" refString="Peruzzi, L, Galasso, G, Domina, G, Bartolucci, F, Santangelo, A, Alessandrini, A, Astuti, G, D'Antraccoli, M, Roma-Marzio, F, Ardenghi, NMG, Barberis, G, Conti, F, Bernardo, L, Peccenini, S, Stinca, A, Wagensommer, RP, Bonari, G, Iamonico, D, Iberite, M, Viciani, D, Del Guacchio, E, Giusso Del Galdo, G, Lastrucci, L, Villani, M, Brunu, A, Magrini, S, Pistarino, A, Brullo, S, Salmeri, C, Brundu, G, Clementi, M, Carli, E, Vacca, G, Marcucci, R, Banfi, E, Longo, D, Di Pietro, R, Passalacqua, NG, 2019. An inventory of the names of native, non-endemic vascular plants described from Italy, their loci classici and types. Phytotaxa 410 (1): 1 - 215, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.410.1.1" title="An inventory of the names of native, non-endemic vascular plants described from Italy, their loci classici and types." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.410.1.1" volume="410" year="2019">Peruzzi et al. (2019)</bibRefCitation>
, and 
<bibRefCitation author="Nikolic, T" journalOrPublisher="Naturalia, Turriers" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B27" refString="Nikolic, T, 2020. Flora Croatica. Vaskularna flora Republike Hrvatske (Vol. 2). Alfa d.d., Zagreb." title="Flora Croatica. Vaskularna flora Republike Hrvatske (Vol. 2). Alfa d. d., Zagreb." year="2020">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Nikolić">Nikolic</normalizedToken>
